Basic TCP chat server written in Java.

Requirments:
  Client Side:
  - can connect, disconnect and reconnect to the server.
  DONE - can send messages to the server.
  - can recieve messages from other clients.
  - can request message history.
  Server Side:
  - save client messages.
  - relay messages to all connected clients.
  - track connected clients.
  CLI functions:
  - list connected clients.
  - connect / disconnect to server.
  - clear chat.
  - retrieve chat history (10/25/50/100 messages).

Possible enhancements:
  - chat rooms
  - private chat
